Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:35.01,Translation,,0,0,0,,Throw away all your fleeting faint desires
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:41.18,Translation,,0,0,0,,And also the thread of hope twisting around your fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:47.94,Translation,,0,0,0,,You won’t be able to follow it any more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:52.17,Translation,,0,0,0,,Enjoy despair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:57.70,Translation,,0,0,0,,You just need to accept “the truth”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:03.16,Translation,,0,0,0,,tucked away in gentle traps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:14.51,Translation,,0,0,0,,Before your dreamlike memories eat it away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:20.28,Translation,,0,0,0,,Burn down the candle of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:30.04,Translation,,0,0,0,,The instant you give up, all meets its end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:36.70,Translation,,0,0,0,,I’m done letting go    of the illusion of you I’m clutching in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:41.40,Translation,,0,0,0,,If the truth is what these eyes can’t see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:47.33,Translation,,0,0,0,,I’m done hesitating   If the answer is somewhere in flux
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:55.59,Translation,,0,0,0,,hiding alongside this blinding pain...
